id":"75bab83b7e28dfefe13faa7d8a964f8bb8a9b3fc","tid":2453794,"uid":256445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T17:22:04.000Z","msg":"咁係幾時同乜野情況下幻滅嘅呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T02:15:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2B8bzZB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2B8bzZB.jpg&h=b5e5640b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗起呢張圖 我覺得係喺第一次長大嘅時候 細個覺得自己會同其他人唔同 可以長生不死 但第一次長大就明白自己其實都係人類一個都會死<br />\n<br />\n至於係幾時 我應該係中學果陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而咩情況就好難講 其實我覺得係一個逐漸嘅過程 當經歷過唔同嘅事 例如親人去世咁 就意識到其實自己好渺小 唔係想像中咁特別 真係無能為力"},{"pid":"9b49206d66b7a4e48f4d68a63e782f4e09478130","tid":2453794,"uid":169275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9de7b6f0be5dcc50a14934987c20fbdf16f6995a","tid":2453794,"uid":29423,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T17:33:34.000Z","msg":"我反而會幻想其他人都有讀心術<br />\n然後叫自己內心唔好亂講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T02:16:52.000Z","msg":"我都好似試過 以為人地可以知自己諗緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2287ed4af42a13fe56f37515b253fa62eb978a58","tid":2453794,"uid":98778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T05:46:09.000Z","msg":"黑人就真係有超能力，佢地夜晚唔著衫合埋眼就會隱形"},{"pid":"d912c7ce73e3fcb835ec0c58e5ae358cafa82465","tid":2453794,"uid":375958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9de7b6f0be5dcc50a14934987c20fbdf16f6995a","tid":2453794,"uid":29423,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T17:33:34.000Z","msg":"我反而會幻想其他人都有讀心術<br />\n然後叫自己內心唔好亂講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:48:43.000Z","msg":"真係有<img src=\"/assets/